setTemplate

public B setTemplate(C configuration)
Description copied from interface: ConfigurationBuilder
Sets the given configuration to be the template for this ConfigurationBuilder. That is, where parameters haven't been specified, the corresponding parameter in the template will be used.

Specified by:
